Relax comrade. It's not a negotiation or threaten, it's just a communication between two "co-workers", but for for my group's fame i should play a thug character, I hope you don't be worry, take it easy but important, do what you should do and make us closer.
-----Evans_Lunatic, Represent to the translating group Junko-mama, 20190618 17:21GMT+8.

Good Dawn/Morning/Noon/Afternoon/Dusk/Night comrade, I'm the  manager of internet relation of the translating group Junko-mama, I must apologize first for a severe mistake I made that cause the untranslated of #21&#22 of this gallery. Our gratitude to you for re-uploading our work at this website is available, but the situation now is you must correct your gallery with the correct content or I should forbid your right that using our work. I prefer to the former one and wish an stable relation with YOU.
     -----Evans_Lunatic, Represent to the translating group Junko-mama, 20190618 17:08GMT +8.
Quite a lame one, to be honest.
